Here's a corrected PlantUML component diagram capturing the static architecture of the Matryx Platform, focusing on the general architectural concern:

```plantuml
@startuml matryx_MatryxPlatform

skinparam componentStyle uml2

package "Smart Contract Layer" {
  [MatryxPlatform] as MP
  [MatryxSystem] as MS
  [MatryxForwarder] as MF
  [MatryxToken] as MT
  [LibPlatform] as LP
  [LibCommit] as LC
  [LibTournament] as LT
}

package "JavaScript Interaction Layer" {
  [utils.js] as UTIL
}

package "Testing/Deployment Layer" {
  [test.js] as TEST
  [benchmark.js] as BENCH
  [leAutomatedPreload.js] as PRELOAD
}

MP --> LP : delegates
MP --> LC : delegates
MP --> LT : delegates

MF <|-- MP : inherits

MS --> MP : manages

UTIL --> MP : interacts
UTIL --> MT : interacts

TEST --> UTIL : uses
BENCH --> UTIL : uses
PRELOAD --> UTIL : uses

@enduml
```